		<p class="contenthead">QR Tracking</p>
		<p class="contenttext">As the world is heading towards a mobile revolution, India is not staying behind. In India mobile phones are poised to become more important than Internet over desktop; this is where from most of the advertising money is generated. VMC Technologies MCube fits right into that strategy and QR codes fits perfectly in the area of engaging customers in the most effective way. Today most mobile phones can scan QR codes. Get a QR Reader here.</p>
		<p class="contenttext">VMC MCube's QRTrack codes are trackable QR Codes. One scan of QRTrack code will direct users to their</p>
		<ul class="bulletpoints">
			<li>Chosen web page</li>
			<li>Link to Google Map or a YouTube Video or your website</li>
			<li>Click to Callback or schedule a callback</li>
			<li>Or Anywhere you like</li>
		</ul> 
		<p class="contenttext">Great news is that you can change this information on the fly without regenerating your QRTrack code . This will save money spent on printing and advertising the regenerated QR Code. Think of QRTrack as your logo your web address, once advertised it is out there and you may not need  to change it even if information underneath changes. Standard QR Code generator's do not allow this, however for a low monthly fee you can generate one QRTrack code and keep it unchanged by changing the profile when required. Not only this QRTrack Code will also give you valuable information like:</p>

		<ul class="bulletpoints">
			<li>Date and Time of each scan</li>
			<li>Number of scan's for your code in last seven days, since inception or within a date range</li>
			<li>Location of scan</li>
			<li>OS or Device of scan</li>
			<li>Campaign associated to QR Code</li>
		</ul> 
		<p class="contenttext">Using this information you can run ad campaigns more effectively. </p>
		<p class="contenttext">QRTrack's QR version for retail industry allows you to generate the coupons on the fly and track them. These discount coupon's can change daily without the need to regenerate the QR Code.</p>
		<p class="contenttext">QRTrack also offer's the basic QR generation for free for anyone who would like to use this technology to help advertise / promote their business using QR. All the user has to do is register, login, generate QR Code and download the generated QR code and use it anywhere you like, the free QR Codes are not tracable, however are still a code mode for engaging with your customers. </p>
		<p class="contenttext">QRTrack codes can be used almost anywhere or any industry to engage offline media advertisement or box of cereal or anything else to online media using the QR and mobile technology.</p>
