		 <li><b>Magazine/Newspaper Ad: </b>Scan the code to launch a how to video, online satisfaction survey etc. Scanning the code can launch digital content such as video for a car model and then lead the user to schedule a test drive or fix an appointment or click to call to get more information.</li>
		 <li><b>Outdoor Billboard or Magazine Ad: </b>Great for a teaser campaign for a new movie. Scan the code to watch the trailer. Or a builder taking clients to show 360 degree view of the upcoming new property.</li>
